two~
THE PRIEST OF ENAERAI

In the temple of Enaerai in Earendam, a priest tends the altar.  He will
also occasionally grant his blessings and spells upon Knights who are in the
temple.  

Like most temple priests, he can heal for a price, but he\@ll also grant
benedictions and heal wounds for Knights, of his own accord, and when his
duties permit.  

The priest will also hold items for the Knights, though he will drop
artifacts of great power (such as the Stones of Power) as such items have
the potential to influence the balance and should not be in the temple.  

If a Knight wishes to request the last item given to the priest, the Knight
may do the following: 

request

Finally, when a Knight prays in the presence of the priest in the temple,
the Knight will be able to discern whether Enaerai is near to the realm of
mortals and the prayer is heard, or whether she is distant.  If she is
distant, the priest will take note of the prayer, and Enaerai will receive
the prayer at a later time, when she once more draws near to the mortal
realm.  
~
