#22086
A Small Trail~
The trail narrows sharply as it descends between two steep walls of
stone, forming a nearly-enclosed crevice.  To the north, the trail runs
along the crevice floor, passing over and around the rocky projections and
boulders.  To the east, the trail is much smoother, broadening into a glade
of tall pines.  
